{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/observer-pattern/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Observer Pattern  Problem…","html":"<h1>Observer Pattern</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d66f5921d7d3ecf6b53b22504fe1af1d/6af66/observer-pattern-img.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.65822784810127%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"observer-pattern\"\n        title=\"observer-pattern\"\n        src=\"/static/d66f5921d7d3ecf6b53b22504fe1af1d/f058b/observer-pattern-img.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d66f5921d7d3ecf6b53b22504fe1af1d/c26ae/observer-pattern-img.png 158w,\n/static/d66f5921d7d3ecf6b53b22504fe1af1d/6bdcf/observer-pattern-img.png 315w,\n/static/d66f5921d7d3ecf6b53b22504fe1af1d/f058b/observer-pattern-img.png 630w,\n/static/d66f5921d7d3ecf6b53b22504fe1af1d/6af66/observer-pattern-img.png 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Problem</h2>\n<p>어느 한 고객이 새로운 제품의 재고확인을 위해 매일같이 스토어에 방문한다고 가정해 봅시다.</p>\n<p>매일같이 방문하는 것은 너무 비효율적인 것 같습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 305px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e88d0ecc73589b5cfc77d08390f92b84/a3e09/observer-pattern-store.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 98.10126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"observer-pattern-store\"\n        title=\"observer-pattern-store\"\n        src=\"/static/e88d0ecc73589b5cfc77d08390f92b84/a3e09/observer-pattern-store.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e88d0ecc73589b5cfc77d08390f92b84/c26ae/observer-pattern-store.png 158w,\n/static/e88d0ecc73589b5cfc77d08390f92b84/a3e09/observer-pattern-store.png 305w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 305px) 100vw, 305px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>언제 재고가 들어올지 정확하게 모르고, 그렇다고 너무 자주가기에는 시간이 없고,,</p>\n<p>그럼 우리는 사장님한테 이렇게 말할거 같아요, 재고가 들어오면 <strong>(상태변화)</strong> 이 번호로 연락을 달라고 <strong>(구독)</strong></p>\n<p>이게 옵저버 패턴입니다.</p>\n<h2>Solution</h2>\n<p>그런데 사장님 입장에서는 고객이 이 사람만 있는게 아니기 때문에 어떤 고객이 재입고 정보를 알고 싶은지 알아야합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 608px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/57ebcdc21b30caffdc617958281a6296/18872/observer-pattern-diagram.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.35443037974683%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"observer-pattern-diagram\"\n        title=\"observer-pattern-diagram\"\n        src=\"/static/57ebcdc21b30caffdc617958281a6296/18872/observer-pattern-diagram.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/57ebcdc21b30caffdc617958281a6296/c26ae/observer-pattern-diagram.png 158w,\n/static/57ebcdc21b30caffdc617958281a6296/6bdcf/observer-pattern-diagram.png 315w,\n/static/57ebcdc21b30caffdc617958281a6296/18872/observer-pattern-diagram.png 608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>옵저버 패턴에서는 구독이라는 방식을 통해 문제를 해결합니다.</p>\n<p>어떠한 상태값의 변동을 원하는 객체는 옵저버 구독을 통해 변동에 대한 값을 받을 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>객체에 직접 물어보는 방식이 아닌 객체가 알아서 알려주는 방식이라고 보시면 됩니다.</p>\n<p>이렇게 되면 구독, 구독해지를 통해 쉽게 연결을 관리할 수 있고 두 객체간의 결합도를 매우 낮출 수 있습니다. <strong>(느슨한 결합)</strong></p>\n<h2>Code</h2>\n<h4>NewsPublisher.java 공급자, 사장님 구현코드</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token import\"><span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>util<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n  \n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsPublisher</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Publisher</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Observer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> observers<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> title<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsPublisher</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t\tobservers <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayList</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t\ttitle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t\tnews <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n  \n\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Override</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">registerObserver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Observer</span> observer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\tobservers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>observer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t  \n\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Override</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">removeObserver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Observer</span> observer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\tobservers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">remove</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>observer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t  \n\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Override</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">notifyObservers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Observer</span> observer <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> observers<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t\tobserver<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">update</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>title<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">setNews</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> title<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> title<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>news <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token function\">notifyObservers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> </code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>registerObserver()</strong> 로 구독을 진행하고<br>\n<strong>removeObserver()</strong> 로 구독을 해제할 수 있습니다.<br>\n<strong>notifyObservers()</strong> 로 구독한 사람에게만 news를 전송합니다.</p>\n<h4>NewsSubscriber.java 구독자, 고객 구현코드</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsSubscriber</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Observer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> observerName<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Publisher</span> publisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsSubscriber</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> subscriber<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Publisher</span> publisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>observerName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> subscriber<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>publisher <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> publisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\tpublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">registerObserver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n\t  \n\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Override</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">update</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> title<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>news <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> title <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"!!! \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token function\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n\t  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"=== \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> observerName <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" 수신 내용 ===\\n\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> news <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>생성자에서 어떤 뉴스를 구독할 지 주입하게 됩니다.<br>\n구독자의 <strong>setNews()</strong> 호출 시 변경된 상태에 대해 데이터를 받아 출력합니다.</p>\n<h4>Main.java 실행코드</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Main</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n  \n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> args<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">NewsPublisher</span> newsPublisher <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsPublisher</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t  \n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">NewsSubscriber</span> newsSubscriber1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsSubscriber</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"구독자 1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> newsPublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">NewsSubscriber</span> newsSubscriber2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NewsSubscriber</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"구독자 2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> newsPublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t  \n\tnewsPublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setNews</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"날씨\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"내일 아침 '영하 8도'..모레 낮부터 누그러져\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\tnewsPublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setNews</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"금융\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\\"5년 만기 부담\\\"…청년 현실 외면하는 청년금융상품\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t  \n\tnewsPublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeObserver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>newsSubscriber1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\tnewsPublisher<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setNews</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"경제\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"고금리 못 버텨…빚 못갚아 경매 넘어간 부동산 급증\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4>결과</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">=== 구독자 1 수신 내용 ===\n날씨!!! 내일 아침 '영하 8도'..모레 낮부터 누그러져\n\n=== 구독자 2 수신 내용 ===\n날씨!!! 내일 아침 '영하 8도'..모레 낮부터 누그러져\n\n=== 구독자 1 수신 내용 ===\n금융!!! \"5년 만기 부담\"…청년 현실 외면하는 청년금융상품\n\n=== 구독자 2 수신 내용 ===\n금융!!! \"5년 만기 부담\"…청년 현실 외면하는 청년금융상품\n\n=== 구독자 2 수신 내용 ===\n경제!!! 고금리 못 버텨…빚 못갚아 경매 넘어간 부동산 급증</code></pre></div>\n<p>두명의 구독자를 생성 후 <strong>NewsPublisher</strong>의 상태가 변경될 때마다 구독자는 데이터를 수신받습니다.<br>\n<strong>newsPublisher.removeObserver(newsSubscriber1)</strong> 이후에는 구독자 2만이 수신받게 됩니다.<br>\n코드상에서 <strong>NewsSubscriber</strong> 는 생성시 구독정보만 주입할 뿐 어떠한 행위를 하지 않았습니다.</p>\n<h2>Applicability</h2>\n<p><strong>옵서버 패턴은 한 객체의 상태가 변경되어 다른 객체들을 변경해야 할 필요성이 생겼을 때, 그리고 실제 객체 집합들을 미리 알 수 없거나 이러한 집합들이 동적으로 변경될 때 사용하기에 적합한 패턴입니다.</strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Observer Pattern","tags":["design pattern","observer pattenr","2024"],"date":"January 30, 2024","description":"여러 객체에 자신이 관찰 중인 객체에 발생하는 모든 이벤트에 대하여 알리는 구독 메커니즘을 정의할 수 있도록 합니다."}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"마이크로 프론트엔드"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/마이크로 프론트엔드/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP 구조에 대해"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/HTTP 1.1/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/observer-pattern/","prevSlug":"/blog/마이크로 프론트엔드/","nextSlug":"/blog/HTTP 1.1/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2714594843","3159585216"]}